Parliament, Monday, 29 October 2018 – The Portfolio Committee on Justice and Correctional Services will tomorrow, 30 October 2018, receive a briefing on the Child Justice Amendment Bill and deliberate on the Cybercrimes and Cybersecurity Bill. Details are as follows: 
	
	Date: Tuesday, 30 October 2018
	Time: 10:00
	Venue: Committee Room 2, Ground Floor, 120 Plein Street Building ISSUED BY THE PARLIAMENTARY COMMUNICATION SERVICES ON BEHALF OF THE CHAIRPERSON OF THE PORTFOLIO COMMITTEE ON JUSTICE AND CORRECTIONAL SERVICES, MS MADIPOANE REFILOE MOREMADI MOTHAPO For media enquiries or interviews, please contact the Committee’s Media Officer: Name: Rajaa Azzakani (Ms)
	Tel: 021 403 8437
	Cell: 081 703 9542
